{"tid":1436910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港人好波】6.12基金籌逾4,900萬 正跟進411個被捕醫療等個案","createTime":"2019-08-09T11:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T11:37:51.000Z","uid":167548,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e37dea931cc5dfc2cc0caad4fc257d82080c2429","tid":1436910,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:33:44.000Z","msg":"為幫助在反送中運動中被捕和受傷的抗爭者，民間早前成立「612人道支援基金」，為抗爭者提供援助。基金今日發表工作簡報，交待由創立至8月8日的工作概要。簡報指基金至今一共籌得超過4,900萬元，過去共批出逾86萬元款項。基金指目前正跟進178個被捕個案、83個醫療支援個案等411個個案。 <br />\n<br />\n基金開支中，開支最大的一項為「緊急經濟支援/撫恤金」，支出接近37萬。基金解釋，會為受傷、被捕或相關人士按個別情況提供一次性緊急經濟支援，亦會為不幸身故死者的直系家屬酌情提供撫恤金。開支排第二的為「項目支援」，用作支援與反送中有關的活動及平台，包括梁凌杰先生的喪禮。<br />\n<br />\n雖然基金正跟進178個被捕個案，但法律支出有49,000元。基金解釋稍後才會收到更多法律費用單據，重申會盡力協助所有被捕及被告者的法律需要，但為保護被捕者私隱，不會公開個別個案的跟進進度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190809/59915225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190809%2F59915225&d=mdS8n1K3gC4RK9SJ0KjOq5q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=3ced8bb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190809%2F59915225&h=c1b9f752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190809/59915225</a><br />\n<br />\n現時拉左580個, 平均一個人得大約8萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">捐夠個一億<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"78015688bbe499ebabcc0b6b8a18fc42d535b3bb","tid":1436910,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a213976ec27984d5a93fdbd32d70d01bf0551e74","tid":1436910,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b642238bc57be723bf8329cd22a295f76b7964e","tid":1436910,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af419cebda3aa786ee56f79e165246d63c87e1b8","tid":1436910,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efaafa6b5f1fb5ecc943ba6775823ddc64b758b5","tid":1436910,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:35:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4cdea560eaa7c0092997d7557dcc1ae2022be85d","tid":1436910,"uid":302000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:37:14.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" 